title: UEFA Champions League Highlights - 19th August 2015
description:
SPORT: UEFA Champions League Highlights
On: itv HD     
Date: Wednesday 19th August 2015 
Time: 22:40 to 23:40

Mark Pougatch presents highlights of the week's UEFA Champions League play-off, first-leg matches as Manchester United make their return to European football after a year away. Manager Louis van Gaal will expect his expensively-assembled side to take a big step towards qualification for the group stage. Also featuring matches involving Valencia, Lazio, Bayer Leverkusen and teams who have made it through the third qualifying round. Studio analysis is provided by Lee Dixon and Gordon Strachan, and commentary comes from Clive Tyldesley.
